data_table.description: The sample attributes I file includes the sample ID, lab ID comprising the sentrix processing ID and position, body site, analyte type, histological type, tumor status, and laboratory in which methylation assays were conducted.

variable.name: SAMPID
variable.description: SHARE subject ID and substudy phs accession number

variable.name: LABID
variable.description: Sample ID based on Lab work and or Sentrix_ID and Sentrix_Position

variable.name: BODY_SITE
variable.description: Tissue from which sample was collected

variable.name: HISTOLOGICAL_TYPE
variable.description: Cell or tissue type or subtype of sample

variable.name: CENTER
variable.description: Laboratory at which methylation assays were conducted
